Insider Activity


Individual




J. Thomas Bentley



Mr. J. T. Bentley is on the Board of Directors at Rambus, Inc., Nanometrics, Inc. and American Foundation for Suicide Prevention. Mr. Bentley was previously employed as a Managing Director by SVB Alliant and a Principal by Berkley International LLC. He also served on the board at Cortina Systems, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from Vanderbilt University and a graduate degree from Massachusetts Institute of Technology.



